Our California-cool Montecito project blends indoor-outdoor living seamlessly + we couldn’t be more pleased to finally share all its beauty! With an amazing team and stunning views, you won’t want to miss this! Check out @thehavenlist for more on this beautiful home! #brandonarchitects

___________________________
Builder: @rdm_general_contractors

•Maximize that space 🙌🏼 one of our favorite things when it comes to designing homes is making the most of a floor plan + how it utilizes every square inch of the land it sits upon! When it comes to these tighter Flower Street lots, it’s all about the perfect transition from one space to another and with pocketing doors leading to this relaxing courtyard, that flow is never interrupted!• #brandonarchitects⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
